metadata.name: Impasto Dreams I
metadata.description:
'Impasto Dreams' invites us on a journey through a landscape of the imagination, rendered in thick, luscious strokes of paint.

These highly abstract works tantalize the senses, inviting us to touch the raised, textured surfaces and lose ourselves in the swirling, vibrant colors.

Each piece is a feast for the eyes, that convey emotion and bring the intangible world of the imagination to life.

'Impasto Dreams' is a collection that will leave you longing for more.
